				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%C3%A1t-ai-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-5-T%E1%BA%B7ng-b%C3%AD-th%C6%B0-gi%C3%A1m-Giang-H%E1%BA%A1-L%C3%BD-c%C3%B4ng-Ung/poem-Qu1ia6IYu7v8HffB5dNOyA">Bát ai thi kỳ 5 - Tặng bí thư giám Giang Hạ Lý công Ung - 八哀詩其五－贈秘書監江夏李公邕</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Vi%C3%AAm/B%C3%A1t-thanh-Cam-Ch%C3%A2u-K%C3%BD-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Quan-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1p-tuy%E1%BA%BFt-s%E1%BB%B1-thanh-du/poem-UgHd2-VrVJf2tv-Uyjpk_w">Bát thanh Cam Châu - Ký Ngọc Quan đạp tuyết sự thanh du - 八聲甘州－記玉關踏雪事清遊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Vi%C3%AAm/author-M_XPpOUpF8GZqWE9vo6bVg">Trương Viêm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Di%E1%BB%85m/Bi-ph%E1%BA%ABn-thi/poem-d-K5myQmQMd-x20ZH01L_w">Bi phẫn thi - 悲憤詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Di%E1%BB%85m/author-EhbmJp2hi9HLiXQfO6maGA">Thái Diễm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c/B%E1%BB%93-t%C3%A1t-man-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-oBMnqsH9trMguAVqCpzukw">Bồ tát man kỳ 2 - 菩薩蠻其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c/author-x2jHtUhu4KZY4kl0A-lAIw">Lý Dục</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%E1%BB%93i-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-qu%E1%BA%A3ng-v%C4%83n-du-H%C3%A0-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-qu%C3%A2n-s%C6%A1n-l%C3%A2m-k%E1%BB%B3-7/poem-OY9RXFNRsvsX5l_jTuzr3A">Bồi Trịnh quảng văn du Hà tướng quân sơn lâm kỳ 7 - 陪鄭廣文遊何將軍山林其七</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-thu/poem-neR2strHTTWqHUGOFqjIbg">Thương thu - 傷秋</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%A9-Nghi%E1%BB%87p/Uy%C3%AAn-h%E1%BB%93-kh%C3%BAc/poem-aw_k9y8xFFL9IBn8k3lN1A">Uyên hồ khúc - 鴛湖曲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%A9-Nghi%E1%BB%87p/author-clxY5GFWegDsEw0Y8VPiNQ">Ngô Vĩ Nghiệp</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
